1.0.name: wordpress/training-tab
1.0.description: Training Tab is a WordPress plu­gin designed to assist admin­is­tra­tors who have train­ing doc­u­men­ta­tion for their end-users in the form of writ­ten doc­u­men­ta­tion, images, links and video instruc­tions. Post train­ing on your cus­tom WordPress site in train­ing tab to make learn­ing and using WordPress easy for your end-users. The plu­gin also allows for end-users to request new train­ing, either from TechStudio or any other developer.
